additionalProperty.value: Delicious and crispy preparation filled with boiled potatoes and spices. Punjabi Samosa Ingredients: Potatoes , Wheat Flour , Refined Sunflower Oil, Water, Green Peas, Interesterified Vegetable Fat (Sesame Oil, Palm Oil), Salt, Spices (Coriander, Cumin, Red Chilli Powder, Mango Powder, Black Pepper, Turmeric, Ajwain, Carom Seeds), Coriander Leaves, Green Chilli. Khatti Meethi Chutney Ingredients: Sugar, Water, Dried Mango Slices, Salt, Red Chilli Powder, Ginger Powder and Spices (Coriander, Cumin, Black pepper, Cardamom, Clove, Cinnamon). Pudina Chutney Ingredients: Coriander Leaves , Water, Mint Leaves, Green Chilli, Peanuts, Cashews, Salt, Black Salt, Cumin, Fresh Lime Juice.
